âš™ï¸ Model Training

1) Used YOLO object detection architecture
2) Dataset annotated with bounding boxes
3) Model trained on labeled blood cell images
4) Best performing weights saved as best.pt

ğŸ§ª Inference
 The trained model can:
1) Detect blood cells in unseen images
2) Draw bounding boxes around detected cells
